      <lineage>
        <LI_Lineage>
          <statement>
            <gco:CharacterString>
              1. Soil interpretation ratings (FSI class, FSI value, OM class, OM value)
                 fetched via SDA tabular REST API using dominant-condition SQL aggregation.
              2. Map unit polygon geometry fetched via SDA spatial REST API (mupolygongeo,
                 WGS84), chunked by survey area to stay within SDA response limits.
              3. County area-weighted averages computed by spatial intersection of SSURGO
                 map unit polygon centroids against US Census TIGER/Line county boundaries.
              4. Vector tiles (PMTiles format) generated by tippecanoe, zoom levels 7-10,
                 served via GitHub Pages.
              5. Update frequency: quarterly, following SSURGO update cycles.
            </gco:CharacterString>
          </statement>
        </LI_Lineage>
      </lineage>
